For the peppered goats' cheese, roll the cubes of cheese in black pepper to coat on all sides.Heat the olive oil in a small frying pan and fry the cheese until golden-brown and crisp on all sides.For the rocket salad,  place the rocket in a bowl and drizzle over the oil and vinegar. Season with salt and freshly ground black pepper and stir well to coat the leaves.To serve, place the rocket salad onto a plate and top with the peppered goats' cheese and beetroot.